data.name: ReportPrintOption
desc: Specifies whether a page header or footer is printed on the same page as the report header or report footer.

items.name: ALL_PAGES
lines: The page header/footer is printed on all pages.

items.name: NOT_WITH_REPORT_HEADER
lines: The page header/footer is not printed on the same page as the report header.

items.name: NOT_WITH_REPORT_FOOTER
lines: The page header/footer is not printed on the same page as the report footer.

items.name: NOT_WITH_REPORT_HEADER_FOOTER
lines: The page header/footer is not printed on the same page as the report header or footer.
